        "created_at": "2020-12-10T02:48:13.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Charming wine, very different than the Ramonet reds, with a bit more darker exotic aromas on the nose.  Very transparent and pure, with beautiful lightness and generous fruit on the palate and a very long finish.  This isn\u2019t a very dense or heavy wine but very lithe and enjoyable.</p>",
